channel.title: Getting my client to have 600+ models/items/anims/gfx
channel.description:
I need help getting my client to have 600+ models/items/anims/gfx.
If one of you is willing to take the time using teamviewer to hook me up, that would be much appreciated.
I'm not sure if this is allowed, but I am willing to pay [b]5.00$[/b] to the person who succesfully solves my problem.
I got paypal, and as you can see you can trust me since I have donated to rune-server myself. (user: parkview111)
Thanks !
ps. I've been trying to do this all afternoon, I put the .gzip into index1 folder in my cache, and in the startup ran unpackModels(1); or what ever the statement is.
